{
  "chapter": 4,
  "chapter_summary": "龙舌剑林佩奇北上潇湘堡请出玉剑萧凌同赴北京，途中听闻终南大侠郁达夫重现江湖，遂折返江南寻访，与萧凌在石门桥分手。林佩奇遍寻郁达夫不果，忧心如焚奔回北京，却发现镇远镖局已被官府查封。原来金刚掌司徒项城竟是独行盗，巨案败露后镖局封门，两河名捕金眼雕田丰也离奇身死。林佩奇在镖局门前偶遇古浊飘，方知其真实身份竟是宰相公子。古浊飘将林佩奇及孙清羽等武林人士安置在相府。孙清羽试探古浊飘武功，发现其深不可测，疑云丛生。众人议论残金毒掌去向与萧凌失踪。回溯前夜，萧凌目睹残金毒掌杀死司徒项城后被其喝退，愤而出城，遇一黑衣蒙面人引至郊外废宅。萧凌在废宅中发现其父飞英神剑萧旭留下的亲笔字条，命她速返江南勿泄漏其行踪。萧凌困惑之际突染重疾，孤零零地倒在废宅床上，陷入病危。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_pei_qi",
      "speaker_name": "林佩奇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "其实我又何尝不累呢？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 25
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_zhuo_piao",
      "speaker_name": "古浊飘",
      "listener": "char_lin_pei_qi",
      "text": "林大侠久违了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_pei_qi",
      "speaker_name": "林佩奇",
      "listener": "char_gu_zhuo_piao",
      "text": "古兄，这究竟是怎么回事？小弟去了江南一趟，离开此地不过才只月余，怎的这里竟有这么多变故？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_zhuo_piao",
      "speaker_name": "古浊飘",
      "listener": "char_lin_pei_qi",
      "text": "说来话长，林兄且莫着急，请随同小弟回到舍下详谈，一切就都明白了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_zhuo_piao",
      "speaker_name": "古浊飘",
      "listener": "char_lin_pei_qi",
      "text": "到了，到了！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_zhuo_piao",
      "speaker_name": "古浊飘",
      "listener": "char_lin_pei_qi",
      "text": "这里就是小弟的寒舍，林兄且请进去！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_pei_qi",
      "speaker_name": "林佩奇",
      "listener": "char_gu_zhuo_piao",
      "text": "小人不知道您竟是宰相公子，还望公子恕罪。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_zhuo_piao",
      "speaker_name": "古浊飘",
      "listener": "char_lin_pei_qi",
      "text": "林兄切莫这等称呼，这样一来，小弟倒难以为情了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_ding",
      "speaker_name": "家丁",
      "listener": "char_gu_zhuo_piao",
      "text": "公子回来了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_zhuo_piao",
      "speaker_name": "古浊飘",
      "listener": "char_lin_pei_qi",
      "text": "到了里面，我给你看几位朋友。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_pei_qi",
      "speaker_name": "林佩奇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来你们全在这里，倒叫——",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_pei_qi",
      "speaker_name": "林佩奇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "司徒大哥呢？潇湘堡的萧姑娘呢？镖局子里到底出了什么事？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_zhuo_piao",
      "speaker_name": "古浊飘",
      "listener": "char_lin_pei_qi",
      "text": "林兄先请坐下来说话。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_pei_qi",
      "speaker_name": "林佩奇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们快说呀！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_qing_yu",
      "speaker_name": "孙清羽",
      "listener": "char_lin_pei_qi",
      "text": "林老三还是这样火烧眉毛的脾气，事情到了这种地步，你急有什么用？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_pei_qi",
      "speaker_name": "林佩奇",
      "listener": "char_sun_qing_yu",
      "text": "事情究竟到了怎样的地步？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_pei_qi",
      "speaker_name": "林佩奇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "唉！司徒大哥怎么会这么做，怎么会这么做！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_pei_qi",
      "speaker_name": "林佩奇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那萧姑娘又跑到什么地方去了？唉！这真是……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 145
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_qi",
      "speaker_name": "孙琪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不管那个残金毒掌武功再好、再厉害、再毒，我若遇到了他，拼命也得和他干一下。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_qing_yu",
      "speaker_name": "孙清羽",
      "listener": "char_sun_qi",
      "text": "琪儿，当着公子的面，你怎么能这样无理！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_zhuo_piao",
      "speaker_name": "古浊飘",
      "listener": "char_sun_qing_yu",
      "text": "没关系，没关系，各位就拿我当古浊飘好了，不要当做别人。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_qing_yu",
      "speaker_name": "孙清羽",
      "listener": "char_gu_zhuo_piao",
      "text": "公子莫怪他，自从他哥哥死后，他整个人就好像变了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_pei_qi",
      "speaker_name": "林佩奇",
      "listener": "char_sun_qi",
      "text": "怎么，难道……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_qi",
      "speaker_name": "孙琪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大哥也是中了那厮一掌，已经故去一个月了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_qing_yu",
      "speaker_name": "孙清羽",
      "listener": "char_gu_zhuo_piao",
      "text": "你不要以为瞒得过我，看，这一下你跑到哪里去。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_qing_yu",
      "speaker_name": "孙清羽",
      "listener": "char_nie_fang_biao",
      "text": "输了吧？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nie_fang_biao",
      "speaker_name": "聂方标",
      "listener": "char_sun_qing_yu",
      "text": "老爷子果然高明，我这盘棋又输了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_zhuo_piao",
      "speaker_name": "古浊飘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "棋局本如人生，一着之错，满盘皆输，聂兄若小心些，或也不至输得这么快。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_zhuo_piao",
      "speaker_name": "古浊飘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但是该输棋的，迟早总得输！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_qing_yu",
      "speaker_name": "孙清羽",
      "listener": "char_gu_zhuo_piao",
      "text": "公子卓论，果然不同凡响，棋局确如人生，一步也走错不得呢。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_zhuo_piao",
      "speaker_name": "古浊飘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "各位不妨就在此安住，静待事情的变化好了，如有所需，只管告诉小弟，千万不要见外。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_pei_qi",
      "speaker_name": "林佩奇",
      "listener": "char_gu_zhuo_piao",
      "text": "公子太客气了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_zhuo_piao",
      "speaker_name": "古浊飘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "各位俱是江湖好汉，小弟倾心已久，平日想请都请不到，今日适逢此事，小弟自应稍尽绵薄之力的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_qing_yu",
      "speaker_name": "孙清羽",
      "listener": "char_gu_zhuo_piao",
      "text": "一掷千金无吝色，神州谁是真豪杰，公子的确是快人。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 215
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_zhuo_piao",
      "speaker_name": "古浊飘",
      "listener": "char_sun_qing_yu",
      "text": "孙老英雄过奖了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 221
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_qing_yu",
      "speaker_name": "孙清羽",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我活了这么多年，遇到的高人也不算少，见的世面也很多，可是我却真正看不出此人的来路，唉，若说他身怀绝技，可也不像，若说他全无武功，唉，这又怎么可能呢？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_gong_shao",
      "speaker_name": "黄公绍",
      "listener": "char_sun_qing_yu",
      "text": "你是说……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_qing_yu",
      "speaker_name": "孙清羽",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我就是说他，我老眼若不花，此人的武功，只怕远在你我之上，只是他是相国公子，又跑到何处去学得这一身的武功呢？当今江湖之上，又有谁能教得出他这一身武功呢？除了……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_pei_qi",
      "speaker_name": "林佩奇",
      "listener": "char_sun_qing_yu",
      "text": "我倒没有看出此人有什么绝深武功。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_qing_yu",
      "speaker_name": "孙清羽",
      "listener": "char_lin_pei_qi",
      "text": "但愿如此。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_pei_qi",
      "speaker_name": "林佩奇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "无论如何，此人对我总算是仁至义尽，他是相国公子，又与我们素无仇怨，既不会有意害我们，也不会冀求我们的帮助，管他会不会武功，又和我们有什么关系。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_pei_qi",
      "speaker_name": "林佩奇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "倒是那残金毒掌的来踪去向，还有什么企图？那玉剑萧姑娘，究竟怎么样了？都是我们应该去想想的。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_qing_yu",
      "speaker_name": "孙清羽",
      "listener": "char_lin_pei_qi",
      "text": "这个自然，难道我还不知道？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_pei_qi",
      "speaker_name": "林佩奇",
      "listener": "char_sun_qing_yu",
      "text": "我们大家都听老爷子的安排。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_qing_yu",
      "speaker_name": "孙清羽",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们老呆在这里，也不是路道，据我看，那残金毒掌此刻绝对已离开了北京，这里的三家镖局子都已关门，他还有什么好停留的，至于那玉剑萧凌嘛……唉，我倒也弄不清她到底跑到什么地方去了，也许去找什么朋友，被留住了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_pei_qi",
      "speaker_name": "林佩奇",
      "listener": "char_sun_qing_yu",
      "text": "绝对不会，那玉剑萧凌初出潇湘堡，是个刚刚离开闺门的大姑娘，在北京城会有什么朋友呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nie_fang_biao",
      "speaker_name": "聂方标",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是那天她出镖局的时候，我却明明听得她说去找个父执朋友呀？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_gong_shao",
      "speaker_name": "黄公绍",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "据我所知，这个古浊飘和她就是认得的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_qing_yu",
      "speaker_name": "孙清羽",
      "listener": "char_huang_gong_shao",
      "text": "你怎么知道？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_gong_shao",
      "speaker_name": "黄公绍",
      "listener": "char_sun_qing_yu",
      "text": "程兄也知道，我们……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_gai",
      "speaker_name": "程垓",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们亲自看到他们走在一起说话的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_pei_qi",
      "speaker_name": "林佩奇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但这……这是不可能的呀！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_can_jin_du_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "残金毒掌",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ling",
      "text": "还不快走！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ling",
      "speaker_name": "萧凌",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "text": "你是谁，想干什么？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ling",
      "text": "天快亮了，你站在屋顶上不怕被别人看到吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ling",
      "text": "快回去吧，站在这里干什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    }
  ],
